1:02:25.075 --> 1:02:26.643
Donny?

1:02:27.477 --> 1:02:28.913
Oh.

1:02:28.946 --> 1:02:30.547
Huh.

1:02:30.580 --> 1:02:32.082
(gear shifts)

1:02:38.455 --> 1:02:40.590
What the heck
