MAN: I'm getting paid to learn
how to run a business,

1:03:01.645 --> 1:03:04.314
do things when I want
and how I want,

1:03:04.348 --> 1:03:07.484
get paid more
than some office job.

1:03:07.517 --> 1:03:09.119
I got freedom.

1:03:09.153 --> 1:03:11.255
(siren wailing)

1:03:11.288 --> 1:03:13.023
Freedom from all of it.

1:03:16.526 --> 1:03:18.362
(dog barking)

1:03:18.395 --> 1:03:19.763
(siren wailing continues)

1:03:19.796 --> 1:03:21.531
(man exhales)
